
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,300,400,700,900" rel="stylesheet">

        <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/icon-font.css"> -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
        <!-- <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="img/favicon.png"> -->

        <title>Progoff Intensive Journal Program | For Self-Development</title>
    </head>
    <body>
<!-- @import "phone-nav.kit" -->
        <div class="expand">

            <!-- @import "navigation.kit" -->

            <div class="col-3-of-3">
                <section class="section-inside">
                  <div class="section-inside-header">
                    <h5 class="heading-five">Miscellaneous</h5>
                    <h1 class="heading-one hr-overview">Refer friends</h1>
                  </div>
                  <div class="section-inside-picture refer-picture">
                      <!-- <img src="img/bird.jpg" alt="overview image"> -->
                  </div>

                <div class="section-inside-content">
                  <h1>Refer Your Friends & Associates</h1>

                  <p class="u-margin-top-small-2">
                    Do you know someone who would really benefit from attending an Intensive Journal workshop?
                  </p>
                  <p>
                  The Journal can help practically anyone who has an interest in developing his/her life. Some examples of
                  individuals who are likely to be interested in the method are:
                  </p>

                  <ul>
                  <li>
                    Going through a transition
                  </li>

                  <li>
                   Interested in mind/ body/ spirit connections
                 </li>

                 <li>
                    Looking for ways to increase creativity
                  </li>

                  <li>
                      Interested in working with dreams and imagery
                  </li>
                  <li>
                      Counselors, psychologists, nurses, social workers
                  </li>
                </ul>

                <p class="u-margin-top-small">
                  Many Intensive Journal workshops have been successful for larger groups including:
                   women's/ men's groups, writers, churches, and senior citizens. Consider these as well for referrals.
                </p>

                <p>
                  Personal referrals are very helpful to us in continuing to offer the program.
                </p>

                <p>
                  <!-- Please fill out the <a href="">referral form</a> below and we'll send them introductory literature. -->
                  Please fill out the <strong> referral form below </strong> and we'll send them introductory literature.
                </p>

                <p>
                  Thanks for your help.
                </p>

                <div class="login-form">
                    <h2 class="heading-secondary ma-bt-lg">Refer your friends</h2>

                    <form class="form form--signup">
                        <div class="form__group">
                            <label class="form__label" for="name">Your name</label>
                            <input class="form__input" id="name" type="text" name="name" placeholder="" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form__group">
                            <label class="form__label" for="friend">Friend's name</label>
                            <input class="form__input" id="friend" type="text" name="friend" placeholder="" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form__group">
                            <label class="form__label" for="address">Address</label>
                            <input class="form__input" id="address" type="text" name="address" placeholder="" required>
                        </div>


                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-2-of-4">
                              <div class="form__group nusu">
                                  <label class="form__label" for="city">City</label>
                                  <input class="form__input half" id="city" type="text" name="city" placeholder="" required>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-1-of-4">
                              <div class="form__group nusu">
                                  <label class="form__label" for="state">State</label>
                                  <input class="form__input half" id="state" type="text" name="state" placeholder="" required>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-1-of-4">
                              <div class="form__group nusu">
                                  <label class="form__label" for="state">Zip</label>
                                  <input class="form__input half" id="state" type="text" name="state" placeholder="" required>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>



                         <div class="form__group">
                            <label class="form__label" for="number">Phone number (Optional)</label>
                            <input class="form__input" id="number" type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="123-456-7890">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form__group">
                            <button class="bton bton--green" id="button">Submit</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                </div>


                </section>

                <!-- @import "footer.kit" -->
            </div>



        </div>


        <script src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@4.5.10-0/dist/ionicons.js"></script>

    </body>
</html>
